y $400/mt more than the stem we bought in Houston so the average price came down from what was estimated.  Despite 30 additional voyage days, actual bunker cost only increased by $7k overall.  \n\n \n\nAs per Fixture note, quite a long ongoing discussion with owners about the Master not following our ballast instructions and there is 2 days reserved for offhire which remain under discussion but intention is to deduct from February hire. (Approx $75k)"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-02-03T20:58:56.73","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"offhire agreed with owners less than originally estimated"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-01-05T01:08:41.69","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Offhire updated to reflect master not following orders on ballast leg"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-12-30T17:33:14.373","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"dems updated, port cost topo updated, canal waiting updated"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-12-27T22:44:54.46","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"two disports finished, updated demurrage estimate"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-12-14T17:18:43.193","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"voyage orders revised, added two ports wcmex - no interim port - $152k additional freight (LS)"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-11-30T14:24:42.517","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"estimated stay in Topolobampo extended 18 days due lack of shore tank space - dem rate 33k/d drops TCE but raises PnL 235k"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-11-28T17:48:35.967","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"canal waiting updated"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-11-19T21:11:31.637","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Waiting at canal updated at $33k/day brings TCE down"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-11-16T18:39:15.52","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Days in port extended at dem rate $33k, increases bunkers and brings down TCE"}],"offhireList":[{"id":193108,"dateStartUtc":"2022-11-05T12:00:00","dateEndUtc":"2022-11-05T23:59:00","days":0.49930555555555556,"displayOrder":0,"o